{
  "text": "and (independent of whether β is zero or not) end up with the linear diffusion equation in the respective renormalization process. To make this rigorous we need a suitable Banach spaces X and rigorous control of the iterative process (2.38), and again we refer to [CITATION_1] The diffusive spreading in physical space corresponds to concentration at κ = 0 in Fourier space according to",
